oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Jack Brandon Insurance Agency, Nashville, Tennessee, 1964 May 25
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A view of the landscape, stone wall, and sign at the Jack Brandon Insurance Agency and Campbell Realty, Inc., located at 3208 West End Avenue, Nashville, Tennessee. Circa May 25th, 1964 they were recognized with a City Beautiful Award. Forms part of Record Group 3, Metro Davidson County Photographer. 1 photograph negative : b & w ; 4 x 5 in.
